+
+## Solution
+
+Selected variant: **B — extend existing replayer + shared compaction core in
+`src/state/journal-compaction.ts`** (single replay truth per item 4; one
+protocol implementation shared by engine and CLI per item 9; config follows
+existing `WorkflowDefaults` patterns). Variant A (inline/duplicated logic)
+rejected: guarantees engine/CLI drift. Variant C (generalized checkpoint
+subsystem) rejected: multi-generation retention and batch compaction are
+explicitly out of scope. Decision made autonomously per benchmark
+non-interactive mode.
+
