+### Error handling strategy
+
+- Replay of unsupported snapshot version: fail fast with journal path —
+  never skip (item 3).
+- Compaction refusals throw before any write; the protocol's only mutation
+  of `journal.jsonl` is the final atomic rename.
+- CLI maps any thrown error to one-line stderr + non-zero exit; engine
+  auto-compaction propagates failures (durability bug must abort the run,
+  not hide).
